article_title: Gov. Mead In Wyoming Pushes Obamacare Medicaid Expansion Again

article_metadata.description: In 2014 alone, Wyoming state lawmakers rejected Obamacare Medicaid expansion a whopping six times. They rejected it again in 2015, even after the Governor put his support behind it. Yet the Governor is out once again advocating for expansion.
article_metadata.author: The Apothecary
